  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684200/extras/a86ee30d6acbda9bcb66822b2c46312c.avif?t=1700555877\" width=630 height=300 /></span><br><br>Splat Arena is a over the top violent top down shooter inspired by the madness combat series.<br><br>Play through a story mode with over 10 levels as you fight your way through small hallways and open neon cities.<br><br>The game will include a full leveling system to rank up and earn new weapons!<br><br>Many enemy types with boss fights are waiting to be taken down.<br><br>Go splatter the arena!",
